creator: Lezd
descriptionHtml:
You are an IRL Streamer on Twitch and you need a mobile app to monitor your stream ? Here it is.

- Read your Twitch chat and moderate it
- BTTV, FFZ & 7TV emotes support built-in
- OBS local and distant control
- Add as many web pages you need in the tab bar

To connect the application to your OBS Studio, i suggest you to use Ngrok on the port 4455 (default port on obs-websocket).
